<p class="headerpath" style="text-align: center;"><span class="UI_COMMAND_NOBOLD" id="thinkreshapeMenu.msg+ThinkReshapeMenu+1">Reshape</span><img src="../../../images/general/litarr.gif"><span class="UI_COMMAND_NOBOLD" id="thinkreshapeMenu.msg+ThinkReshapeMenu+18">Insert</span><img src="../../../images/general/litarr.gif"><span class="UI_OPTION_NOBOLD" id="thinkreshapeMenu.msg+ThinkReshapeMenu+36">Mesh Boundaries</span></p>
